      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to see it that way. i look at her and i see her eyes looking so drained. i spent forty years looking after him, and now the roles are all flipped and it just feels wrong. i feel like i've finished my part. i've done my time. it would be so much easier for everyone if they didn't have to worry about my pills and my appointments and my constant needs anymore. it's like i'm just holding them back from their own lives.",
